<plot>Allen Funt takes his hidden camera and microphone to Atlantic City and sneaks upon a black man in a boardwalk salt-water-taffy store. After wearing this situation out, which doesn't take long with Funt, he poses as a beautician in a beauty-shop (which is where beauticians work), and then as a customer under the hair dryer to confuse another customer.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?092705</url></doc>
